jedan nacin sto ih cini predvidljivim.

513
00:50:57,767 --> 00:50:59,200
Prezentracmo im neocekivano.

514
00:51:00,114 --> 00:51:01,388
l gledacemo ih kako se raspadaju.

515
00:51:09,899 --> 00:51:11,059
Disko?

516
00:51:13,544 --> 00:51:14,545
Plasis se.

517
00:51:14,616 --> 00:51:15,696
Naravno da ne.

518
00:51:15,771 --> 00:51:17,932
Nemoj.

519
